data.name: m_btnHelp.HelpString
data.value: Displays a description of the parts and functions of this dialog box.

data.name: m_btnCancel.HelpString
data.value: Closes this dialog box without saving the changes you have made in this dialog. (Changes made in nested dialog boxes are not cancelled).

data.name: m_txtProjDescription.HelpString
data.value: Displays a description of this project for future reference (only in this dialog)

data.name: m_txtProjName.HelpString
data.value: Displays/sets the name of this project.

data.name: m_addWSsToSldrCheckBox.Text
data.value: Allow writing system information to be added to the SIL Locale Data Repository

data.name: m_btnAnalMoveUp.HelpString
data.value: Moves the selected analysis writing system up one position in the list.

data.name: m_btnAnalMoveDown.HelpString
data.value: Moves the selected analysis writing system down one position in the list.

data.name: m_btnDelAnalWs.HelpString
data.value: Removes the selected analysis writing system from the project, but not from FieldWorks. Some text may become hidden. Use the Add button to return the writing system to the project.

data.name: m_btnModifyAnalWs.HelpString
data.value: Opens a dialog so you can modify the features of the selected writing system.

data.name: m_btnAddAnalWs.HelpString
data.value: Opens a menu so you can add a analysis writing system to this project. You may select an existing writing system or define a new one.

data.name: m_btnVernMoveUp.HelpString
data.value: Moves the selected vernacular writing system up one position in the list.

data.name: m_btnVernMoveDown.HelpString
data.value: Moves the selected vernacular writing system down one position in the list.

data.name: m_btnDelVernWs.HelpString
data.value: Removes the selected vernacular writing system from the project, but not from FieldWorks. Some text may become hidden. Use the Add button to return the writing system to the project.

data.name: m_btnModifyVernWs.HelpString
data.value: Opens a dialog so you can modify the features of the selected writing system.

data.name: m_btnAddVernWs.HelpString
data.value: Opens a menu so you can add a vernacular writing system to this project. You may select an existing writing system or define a new one.

data.name: m_lstAnalWs.HelpString
data.value: Displays available analysis writing systems in this project. Selected check boxes indicate those that appear in single-line text fields and their vertical order.

data.name: m_lstVernWs.HelpString
data.value: Displays available vernacular writing systems in this project. Selected check boxes indicate those that appear in single-line text fields and their vertical order.

data.name: label6.Text
data.value: Writing systems defined for this project are shown below. Check those which you want to appear in multilingual, single-line fields. The first checked writing system is the default for its type.

data.name: label13.Text
data.value: Note: If you will collaborate with Send/Receive or by sharing the project over a network connection, use the default folder location.

data.name: btnLinkedFilesBrowse.HelpString
data.value: Opens a dialog so you can find and select the folder for your external files.

data.name: txtExtLnkEdit.HelpString
data.value: Specifies a folder on your machine where external files you link to are stored.

data.name: label11.Text
data.value: Also, keep linked files in one location so that they are all included in the backup files when you back up the project.

data.name: label10.Text
data.value: FieldWorks allows you to set links to files such as documents and pictures.

data.name: m_btnOK.HelpString
data.value: Applies and saves changes you have made and closes this dialog box.

data.name: m_enableProjectSharingCheckBox.Text
data.value: Share project contents with programs on this computer
